#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para><footnote><para>
msgid ""
"<citetitle>Bach</citetitle> v. <citetitle>Longman</citetitle>, 98 Eng. Rep. "
"1274 (1777)."
msgstr ""
"<citetitle>Bach</citetitle> v.<citetitle> Longman</citetitle>, 98 Eng. Rep. "
